🎓 Student Score Prediction

📌 Objective
Predict students' exam scores based on study hours, attendance, motivation, and other academic/social factors.

 📊 Dataset
      - Features: Hours Studied, Attendance, Sleep Hours, Tutoring, etc.
      - Target: `Exam_Score`

🔧 Steps Taken
      - Data cleaning (handle missing values, encoding categorical variables)
      - Exploratory Data Analysis (Heatmap, Scatterplots, Boxplots)
      - Linear Regression model applied
      - Evaluated using Mean Squared Error (MSE) & R² score

🏆 Results
      - Positive correlation between hours studied, attendance, and exam performance
      - Linear Regression provided good predictions


